OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1776041690
OL,3,CDumfriesshire decides: the Scottish
OL,4,Celection candidates wanting your votes
OL,6,FITV Border's Dumfries and Galloway
OL,7,Freporter Natalie Higgins has met the
OL,8,Fcandidates vying for your votes in
OL,9,FDumfriesshire.
OL,11,FThe vast and picturesque constituency
OL,12,Fof Dumfriesshire encompasses towns
OL,13,Flike Moffat, Lockerbie, Annan and
OL,14,FGretna.
OL,16,FBut despite its obvious attractions,
OL,17,Fit's struggling with closures of
OL,18,Fessential services, limited access to
OL,19,Fhealthcare and shrinking communities,
OL,20,Fas younger families move away and
OL,21,Fbirth rates fall.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/19
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
