CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1776041690
OL,3,CDumfriesshire decides: the Scottish
OL,4,Celection candidates wanting your votes
OL,6,FSo what are the candidates promising
OL,7,Fto do to tackle these issues?
OL,9,FScottish Conservatives
OL,11,FOliver Mundell took this seat from
OL,12,FLabour in the 2016 election and has
OL,13,Fheld the position since. He announced
OL,14,Fhe would step down ahead of the 2026
OL,15,Felection, with Craig Hoy, who served
OL,16,Fas a list MSP for South Scotland since
OL,17,F2021, hoping to take the reins.
OL,19,FHowever, national polling suggests the
OL,20,FScottish Conservatives are on course
OL,21,Fto fall behind Reform UK.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/19
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35503
