CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1776041690
OL,3,CDumfriesshire decides: the Scottish
OL,4,Celection candidates wanting your votes
OL,6,FMr Hoy told ITV Border that a vote for
OL,7,Fanyone other than the Conservatives
OL,8,Fwould hand over the seat to the SNP.
OL,10,F"I'll be focused on those bread and
OL,11,Fbutter issues, fixing the roads and
OL,12,Fmaking sure we get the buses back to
OL,13,Fwhere we want them to be," he said.
OL,15,FWhen asked whether he was worried if a
OL,16,FReform vote would split the support
OL,17,Ffor the Conservatives, he said: "I'm
OL,18,Fnot complacent and I recognise there
OL,19,Fis a Reform movement out there.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/19
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1776041690
OL,3,CDumfriesshire decides: the Scottish
OL,4,Celection candidates wanting your votes
OL,6,F"If they vote Reform the likelihood is
OL,7,Fthat they will let the SNP candidate
OL,8,Fwin here and if they win then they can
OL,9,Fwin anywhere in Scotland.
OL,11,F"We will be straight back into the
OL,12,Fterror of another independence
OL,13,Freferendum if that happens."
OL,15,FScottish National Party (SNP)
OL,17,FStanding against the Conservatives for
OL,18,Fthe SNP is the leader of Dumfries and
OL,19,FGalloway Council, Stephen Thompson.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/19
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
