OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1776041690
OL,3,CDumfriesshire decides: the Scottish
OL,4,Celection candidates wanting your votes
OL,6,FHe has been a councillor since 2012
OL,7,Fand argues his political experience
OL,8,Fwill give him a strong voice in
OL,9,FHolyrood for the people of
OL,10,FDumfriesshire.
OL,12,F"The concerns around depopulation,
OL,13,Fagriculture, connectivity, schools and
OL,14,Feducation, childcare - all of those
OL,15,Fthings are important to Dumfriesshire
OL,16,Fand I want to stand up for them at
OL,17,FScottish Parliament."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/19
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
