OL,3,CDumfriesshire decides: the Scottish
OL,4,Celection candidates wanting your votes
OL,6,FThe SNP government has been in power
OL,7,Ffor nearly two decades and in the last
OL,8,Felection promised to expand free early
OL,9,Fyears education to all children two
OL,10,Fand under, but five years on, that's
OL,11,Fnot the case.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/19
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
