OL,3,CDumfriesshire decides: the Scottish
OL,4,Celection candidates wanting your votes
OL,6,FWhen asked about this, Mr Thompson
OL,7,Fresponded: "That provision is there
OL,8,Fbut it can always be improved. I think
OL,9,Fthere's always different political
OL,10,Fpriorities and there will be different
OL,11,Fdecisions over the border but we now
OL,12,Frecognise that this needs to be a
OL,13,Fpriority and that's just the way
OL,14,Fgovernments have to evolve its
OL,15,Fpolicies."
OL,17,FReform UK Scotland
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/19
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
