OL,3,CDumfriesshire decides: the Scottish
OL,4,Celection candidates wanting your votes
OL,6,FDavid Kirkwood is a founder member
OL,7,FReform UK Scotland. He describes
OL,8,Fhimself as a fiercely proud and
OL,9,Fambitious Scot.
OL,11,F"We're not like the rest," he said.
OL,12,F"We're a party of ordinary people and
OL,13,Fwe're fed up with the political
OL,14,Festablishment."
OL,16,FReform want seats at the table in
OL,17,FHolyrood, but last year they were shut
OL,18,Fout of a summit that all other main
OL,19,Fparties were invited to, because the
OL,20,FFirst Minister John Swinney said they
OL,21,Fwere far right.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/19
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1776041690
OL,3,CDumfriesshire decides: the Scottish
OL,4,Celection candidates wanting your votes
OL,6,FWhen asked if the party was far right,
OL,7,FMr Kirkwood said: "No of course we're
OL,8,Fnot. Far right is just somebody that
OL,9,Fthey don't like.
OL,11,F"It's a totally meaningless phrase.
OL,12,FWe're not far right. We're just right."
OL,14,FScottish Labour
OL,16,FLinda Dorward is a Dumfries and
OL,17,FGalloway councillor and was previously
OL,18,Fco-leader of the council when it was
OL,19,Frun in coalition with the SNP.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/19
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
