PN,35510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1776041690
OL,3,CDumfriesshire decides: the Scottish
OL,4,Celection candidates wanting your votes
OL,6,FLabour finished a long way behind the
OL,7,FConservatives and SNP in the 2021
OL,8,Felection, but will the Prime
OL,9,FMinister's unpopularity translate to a
OL,10,Flack of support here in Scotland?
OL,12,FMs Dorward, said: "I'm here for people
OL,13,Fin Dumfries. I think Dumfriesshire had
OL,14,Fbeen missed out for a long time under
OL,15,Fthe SNP government.
OL,17,F"I think Anas Sarwar was right when he
OL,18,Fsaid Keir Starmer should stand down,
OL,19,Fbut it's not about Keir Starmer.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/19
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1776041690
OL,3,CDumfriesshire decides: the Scottish
OL,4,Celection candidates wanting your votes
OL,6,F"Ordinary people are saying they are
OL,7,Fpaying higher taxes and they're seeing
OL,8,Fnothing for it. What they want is
OL,9,Finvestment down here and what they
OL,10,Fwant is recognition for Dumfriesshire."
OL,12,FLiberal Democrats
OL,14,FIain McDonald has lived in Dumfries
OL,15,Fand Galloway most of his life and says
OL,16,Fhe is passionate about what it has to
OL,17,Foffer.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G11/19
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1776041690
OL,3,CDumfriesshire decides: the Scottish
OL,4,Celection candidates wanting your votes
OL,6,FBut in the last election the party
OL,7,Fsecured only 3.2% of the vote,
OL,8,Fcompared to the Conservatives who
OL,9,Freceived 47.7% of votes.
OL,11,FMr McDonald, said: "You want things to
OL,12,Fget done and people who will sit down
OL,13,Fand negotiate with the SNP like we did
OL,14,Fin the budget.
OL,16,F"The Liberal Democrats have pushed
OL,17,Fthings through and they are very
OL,18,Fpassionate about mental health,
OL,19,Fchildren, and schools. We've got to
OL,20,Fget the grassroots sorted."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G12/19
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
