OL,3,CDumfriesshire decides: the Scottish
OL,4,Celection candidates wanting your votes
OL,6,FFull list of candidates standing in
OL,7,Fthe Dumfriesshire constituency:
OL,9,FKey issues for voters in Dumfriesshire
OL,11,FLocal families say childcare costs are
OL,12,Ftoo high and wish support was inline
OL,13,Fwith their English neighbours.
OL,15,FEngland offers working parents of
OL,16,Fchildren aged nine months to school
OL,17,Fage, 15-30 free childcare hours per
OL,18,Fweek.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G13/19
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
