PN,35514
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1776041690
OL,3,CDumfriesshire decides: the Scottish
OL,4,Celection candidates wanting your votes
OL,6,FScotland provides 1,140 funded hours a
OL,7,Fyear, approximately 30 hours a week,
OL,8,Ffor all 3 and 4-year-olds.
OL,10,FOnly about a quarter of two-year-olds
OL,11,Fcurrently qualify, usually those from
OL,12,Fthe lowest income families.
OL,14,FMeghan Carroll from Gretna pays more
OL,15,Fthan #800 a month to send one-year-old
OL,16,FBethany to nursery but if she lived
OL,17,Ffive minutes down the road in England
OL,18,Fit would be fully funded by the
OL,19,Fgovernment.
OL,21,F"Financially it's a lot," Meghan said.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G14/19
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35515
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1776041690
OL,3,CDumfriesshire decides: the Scottish
OL,4,Celection candidates wanting your votes
OL,6,F"It feels like we're being penalised
OL,7,Ffor being working parents when in my
OL,8,Fopinion it should be the opposite,
OL,9,Fespecially when it works out you're
OL,10,Fpaying out more for childcare than you
OL,11,Fare able to earn a wage.
OL,13,F"It doesn't make sense. Just because
OL,14,Fyou work doesn't necessarily mean you
OL,15,Fcan afford to take your children out
OL,16,Fmore than those who receive benefits.
OL,17,FAll children deserve the same
OL,18,Fregardless."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G15/19
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35516
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1776041690
OL,3,CDumfriesshire decides: the Scottish
OL,4,Celection candidates wanting your votes
OL,6,FMeghan is not the only one feeling the
OL,7,Fpressure. Rochelle Jones from Annan
OL,8,Fplans to send her toddler Eddie to
OL,9,Fnursery after the summer but says she
OL,10,Fis dreading the monthly costs.
OL,12,FRochelle, said: "It would have been so
OL,13,Fmuch better for work life balance not
OL,14,Fhaving to pay so much for it.
OL,16,F"Every child no matter where they are
OL,17,Fin the UK should be entitled to the
OL,18,Fsame thing. Childcare doesn't just
OL,19,Fbenefit the parents it benefits the
OL,20,Fchildren so I don't know why all
OL,21,Fchildren can't have that opportunity."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G16/19
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
