OL,3,CDumfriesshire decides: the Scottish
OL,4,Celection candidates wanting your votes
OL,6,FDumfries and Galloway is experiencing
OL,7,Fa significant rural depopulation
OL,8,Fcrisis, with the population falling to
OL,9,Faround 145,000 in recent years.
OL,11,FLack of childcare support in
OL,12,FDumfriesshire can be linked to low
OL,13,Feconomic growth and population
OL,14,Fdecline, prompting calls for priority
OL,15,Ffunding to address these childcare
OL,16,Fgaps.
OL,18,F2021 RESULTS: Dumfriesshire
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G17/19
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
