OL,3,CDumfriesshire decides: the Scottish
OL,4,Celection candidates wanting your votes
OL,6,FOliver Mundell, Scottish Conservative
OL,7,Fand Unionist Party - 47.7% - 19,487
OL,8,Fvotes
OL,10,FJoan McAlpine, Scottish National Party
OL,11,F(SNP) - 37.7% - 15,421 votes
OL,13,FColin Smyth, Scottish Labour - 11.4% -
OL,14,F4,671 votes
OL,16,FRichard Brodie, Scottish Liberal
OL,17,FDemocrats - 3.2% - 1,314 votes
